snippet.title: Dweller's Empty Path
snippet.description:
You can play it at: https://tuyoki.itch.io/dwellers-empty-path !!

---
Here is my second little rpgmaker project I've ever done!! 
This one is quite a bit longer than the last one, it took around a year to make and I'd say the game is maybe an hour long or so. I hope you like it!! (Sorry there's no 2D animation in the game, I just wanted to make it for the promo video)
---

Animation Credits:
By Temmie Chang
Promo animation (All animation, clean-up, design and backgrounds) By Temmie Chang
Music (Production & Arrangement) By Camellia
Music (Melody & Chords) By Toby Fox, Temmie Chang, Camellia


Toby Fox:  https://twitter.com/tobyfox
Camellia: https://twitter.com/cametek , https://cametek.jp/
Temmie Chang: (me) https://twitter.com/tuyoki

The soundtrack is available here! : https://linkco.re/9AManMqf?lang=en
